\description{Takes in a filename in the form of a string of a file in existence or one that will be created. Asks for user's name and opens a file writing the name entered and the Sys.time.  Then asks for user to type more or enter 'q' to quit.  File can be reopened and more can be added by calling the function again.
%%  ~~ A concise (1-5 lines) description of what the function does. ~~
}
